* Rhymes: (''US'') [[Rhymes:English:-aʊt|-aʊt]], (''Commonwealth English'') [[Rhymes:English:-uːt|-uːt]]

====Homophones====
*[[root]] {{italbrac|Commonwealth English}}

===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# The course or way which is traveled or passed, or is to be passed.
# A passing; a course; a road or path; a march.
# The way to do something.

