{{mid}}
{{bottom}}

===Verb===
{{en-verb|rout|ing}}

# To direct or divert along a particular course.
#: The '''route''' was used so much that it formed a [[rut]].
# {{Internet}} to connect two [[local area network|local area networks]], thereby forming an [[internet]]

